title: Jump Then Fall (Taylor's Version)
description:
Hey Kayla! This one is for you! What is Jump Then Fall about? And how did our fellow Swiftie Kayla use this song as an Easter egg on a very special day?
This song wasn't about Taylor squared but the two of them did appear in a movie together, and this song was featured in it! Nick, Ana and Lacey break down this song and discuss the movie that starred Taylor and her boyfriend Taylor!
Kayla hit us up! Feel free to chime in anytime, Swifties!
